XBMC-SHELL - a mplayer lookalike xbmc playlist manager

Dead simple thingie that lets me manage my xbmc from a shell on that machine.

A simple thing as play a album:
xbmc-shell Music/Artist/Album/

Play a specific file:
xbmc-shell Music/song.mp3

Play multiple files

xbmc-shell Music/song1.mp3 Music/song2.mp3

Control the player:
xbmc-shell Pause
xbmc-shell Next
